                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I don't think I have experienced this exactly, but I have had a pet fighting, and die, then recharm that pet and have it instantly run off to finish the job. I learned that if I hit /pet follow and then /pet back off, he would then stay put. I think /pet back off followed by /pet sit worked also.
<br />

<br />
On that occasion, the mobs my pet was fighting, didn't return though, although I was fighting static mobs at the time, not sure if that was the difference.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="font-style: italic">That is all I have to say about that! - Forest Gump</span>
